article_text:
A former Goldman Sachs Group executive will be the new top official of Cushman & Wakefield Inc., a commercial real-estate company.

Edward C. Forst starts Jan. 6 as chief executive and president; the firm's executive chairman, Carlo Barel di Sant'Albano, has served as interim chief executive and president since Glenn Rufrano stepped down in...
